The '''UN Declaration on the Elimination of All Forms of Intolerance and of Discrimination Based on Religion or Belief''' is a [[United Nations]] resolution, passed on November 25 1981.  It outlined [[human rights]] regarding the [[freedom of religion]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.un.org/documents/ga/res/36/a36r055.htm|title=A/RES/36/55.  Declaration on the Elimination of All Forms of Intolerance and of Discrimination Based on Religion or Belief|website=www.un.org|access-date=2017-04-01}}</ref>

